🚀 Flow Extractor - AI Core 🧠

Welcome to the brain of Flow Extractor! This repository hosts the computer vision model that allows the Figma plugin to "understand" and reconstruct designs from images.

🛠 Technical Model Details

⚡ Engine Base: YOLOv8 Nano (Ultralytics)
📦 Format: ONNX Runtime (Opset 12)
🎯 Specialization: Real-time UI/UX element detection.
🎨 Optimization: Quantized for ultra-fast execution in browsers.
🔍 What is it capable of detecting?

🔘 Buttons & CTAs: Identifies rounded and rectangular buttons.
🖼 Images & Containers: Separates photos from solid backgrounds.
📝 Text Blocks: Locates headlines and paragraphs for precision OCR.
✨ Icons: Detects interface glyphs and symbols.
📲 How to integrate it into the Plugin To make the plugin work with this AI, use the direct download URL (Raw):

🛠 Maintenance Instructions To update the model, simply replace the .onnx file while keeping the same name. The plugin will automatically update on the next run.

Powered by Ultralytics YOLOv8 & ONNX Runtime Web 🚀
